  <description><![CDATA[<p>Borovets is a long-established ski resort situated in the atmospheric pine forests of the Rila Mountains. Enjoy the good value and fun environment that the resort has to offer as well as the colourful local traditions that make skiing here a little more unique! The resort's three easily accessible ski areas ensure plenty of variation and interest for all ski abilities. Best served are first-timer or novice skiers who progress under the care of the well regarded instructors. The colourful centre comes to life in the evening, offering numerous typical Bulgarian and continental restaurants, late night bars and live music venues.</p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
