  <generalInformation><![CDATA[<p> <strong>Beginners skiing in Borovets</strong></p>
<p>Progress quickly under the guidance of the English speaking ski school instructors to explore the whole mountain.</p>
<p><strong> </strong></p>
<p><strong>Intermediate skiing in Borovets</strong></p>
<p>A selection of wide open pistes at the top of the gondola lead to long runs through the forest back to the village.</p>
<p><strong> </strong></p>
<p><strong>Advanced skiing in Borovets</strong></p>
<p>The Yastrebets area is the most testing, with a tree lined World Cup run back to resort.</p>
<p><strong> </strong></p>
<p><strong>Snowboarding in Borovets</strong></p>
<p>With excellent instruction available this fun resort lends itself to boarders of all types.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Related links</p>
<ul>
<li>Also in Bulgaria, try <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/resorts/hotels/item72/bansko/">Bansko</a></li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></generalInformation>
